"&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nWritten evidence submitted by Manchester International Festival (MIF) [FB0075]&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n-\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nMIF is supportive of the BBC’s remit to stimulate creativity and cultural excellence and considers the organization to be achieving this aim\n-\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nMIF believes the BBC to be a collaborative\n and risk-taking partner in producing new work\n-\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nThe BBC’s unparalleled arts coverage widens the audience for ambitious new art making the funding and work involved go much further\n-\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \nMIF has found the BBC’s move to Salford to be an extremely positive developme\nnt for the cultural industries in the North West and beyond\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nDecember 2013\n&#xa0;\n"